{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.1","label":"","reference":"Psaumes 41:1","prev_osis_id":"Ps.040.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ps.041.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">(Mt 5:7. Ps 112.) Ps 55.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Ps.41.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Au chef des chantres. Psaume de David.<\/p>\n<p class=\"b\"><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ps.41","name":"Psaumes 41","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.2","name":"Psaumes 41:2","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.40.18","name":"Psaumes 40:18","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.40.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.2","label":"","reference":"Psaumes 41:2","prev_osis_id":"Ps.041.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ps.041.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Ps.41.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Heureux celui qui s\u2019int\u00e9resse au pauvre!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Au jour du malheur l\u2019\u00c9ternel le d\u00e9livre;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ps.41","name":"Psaumes 41","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.3","name":"Psaumes 41:3","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.1","name":"Psaumes 41:1","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.3","label":"","reference":"Psaumes 41:3","prev_osis_id":"Ps.041.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ps.041.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Ps.41.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel le garde et lui conserve la vie.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Il est heureux sur la terre,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et tu ne le livres pas au bon plaisir de ses ennemis.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ps.41","name":"Psaumes 41","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.4","name":"Psaumes 41:4","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.2","name":"Psaumes 41:2","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.4","label":"","reference":"Psaumes 41:4","prev_osis_id":"Ps.041.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ps.041.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Ps.41.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel le soutient sur son lit de douleur;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tu le soulages dans toutes ses maladies.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ps.41","name":"Psaumes 41","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.5","name":"Psaumes 41:5","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.3","name":"Psaumes 41:3","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.5","label":"","reference":"Psaumes 41:5","prev_osis_id":"Ps.041.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ps.041.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Ps.41.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Je dis: \u00c9ternel, aie piti\u00e9 de moi!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Gu\u00e9ris mon \u00e2me! Car j\u2019ai p\u00e9ch\u00e9 contre toi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ps.41","name":"Psaumes 41","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.6","name":"Psaumes 41:6","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.4","name":"Psaumes 41:4","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.6","label":"","reference":"Psaumes 41:6","prev_osis_id":"Ps.041.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ps.041.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Ps.41.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Mes ennemis disent m\u00e9chamment de moi:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Quand mourra-t-il? Quand p\u00e9rira son nom?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ps.41","name":"Psaumes 41","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.7","name":"Psaumes 41:7","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.5","name":"Psaumes 41:5","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.7","label":"","reference":"Psaumes 41:7","prev_osis_id":"Ps.041.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ps.041.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Ps.41.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Si quelqu\u2019un vient me voir, il prend un langage faux,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Il recueille des sujets de m\u00e9dire;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Il s\u2019en va, et il parle au-dehors.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ps.41","name":"Psaumes 41","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.8","name":"Psaumes 41:8","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.6","name":"Psaumes 41:6","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.8","label":"","reference":"Psaumes 41:8","prev_osis_id":"Ps.041.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ps.041.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Ps.41.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Tous mes ennemis chuchotent entre eux contre moi;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ils pensent que mon malheur causera ma ruine:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ps.41","name":"Psaumes 41","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.9","name":"Psaumes 41:9","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.7","name":"Psaumes 41:7","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.9","label":"","reference":"Psaumes 41:9","prev_osis_id":"Ps.041.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ps.041.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Ps.41.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Il est dangereusement atteint,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Le voil\u00e0 couch\u00e9, il ne se rel\u00e8vera pas!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ps.41","name":"Psaumes 41","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.10","name":"Psaumes 41:10","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.8","name":"Psaumes 41:8","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.10","label":"","reference":"Psaumes 41:10","prev_osis_id":"Ps.041.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ps.041.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Ps.41.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Celui-l\u00e0 m\u00eame avec qui j\u2019\u00e9tais en paix,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Qui avait ma confiance et qui mangeait mon pain,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">L\u00e8ve le talon contre moi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ps.41","name":"Psaumes 41","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.11","name":"Psaumes 41:11","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.9","name":"Psaumes 41:9","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.11","label":"","reference":"Psaumes 41:11","prev_osis_id":"Ps.041.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ps.041.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Ps.41.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Toi, \u00c9ternel, aie piti\u00e9 de moi et r\u00e9tablis-moi!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et je leur rendrai ce qui leur est d\u00fb.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ps.41","name":"Psaumes 41","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.12","name":"Psaumes 41:12","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.10","name":"Psaumes 41:10","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.12","label":"","reference":"Psaumes 41:12","prev_osis_id":"Ps.041.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ps.041.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Ps.41.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Je conna\u00eetrai que tu m\u2019aimes,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Si mon ennemi ne triomphe pas de moi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ps.41","name":"Psaumes 41","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.13","name":"Psaumes 41:13","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.11","name":"Psaumes 41:11","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.13","label":"","reference":"Psaumes 41:13","prev_osis_id":"Ps.041.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ps.041.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Ps.41.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Tu m\u2019as soutenu \u00e0 cause de mon int\u00e9grit\u00e9,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et tu m\u2019as plac\u00e9 pour toujours en ta pr\u00e9sence.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ps.41","name":"Psaumes 41","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.14","name":"Psaumes 41:14","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.12","name":"Psaumes 41:12","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.14","label":"","reference":"Psaumes 41:14","prev_osis_id":"Ps.041.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ps.042.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Ps.41.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>B\u00e9ni soit l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, d\u2019\u00e9ternit\u00e9 en \u00e9ternit\u00e9! Amen! Amen!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ps.41","name":"Psaumes 41","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.42.1","name":"Psaumes 42:1","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.42.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ps.41.13","name":"Psaumes 41:13","id":"fra-LSG:Ps.41.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb2c8f317.72408367');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb2c8f317.72408367\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb2c8f317.72408367","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb2c8f317.72408367'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb2c8f317.72408367\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}